column1: Supplementary Data VII. Full ancient genomes dataset
Sample details for all ancient genomes imputed and analysed in this study, including published data (publication source in column 'Data source')
Age (upper), Age (lower), Age average, Dating: radiocarbon date ranges (upper and lower bounds) for 95%CI and mean; dating source (direct date or context)
Y haplogroup major & Y haplogroup derived: Y-chromosomal haplogroup - major clade and derived subclade (where relevant)
Coverage: Autosomal genome gepth of coverage (x)
Average GP: average genotype probability for called and imputed genotypes
Flag: flags used to mark samples in analyses (low coverage; low GP; close relationship to other sample; 0=no flag - see Methods)
IBD clustering: labels used for IBD clustering analysis (see Supplementary Note 3f)
